{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You wanted a requisition-- Montgomery issued an order-- he used to give orders [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, up to now, you've been liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every country you've gone into, you've acted liberators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now you've gone into Germany, you go in as conquerors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Therefore, there's no excuse for any man under my command not to have a decent bed at night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Consequently, all tents will be sent back to headquarters forthwith.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when he said forthwith, he didn't mean you looked up-- put on a pair of kid gloves, look up the Marquess of Queensberry rules of warfare, and see what the next move is.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When he says forthwith, he meant there and then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that, that more or less gave you-- you can requisition what you like.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But these two people, they said they, they were accused of looting two chickens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I had to go pick them up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went into the-- they were still being held in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was stone walls, a massive stone door, like a dungeon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was built like a dungeon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As you came in, there, there was some huts there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was this-- these few cells, which they--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're cells to put people in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I couldn't have been in there more than 10 minutes, a quarter of an hour at the most.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took them back to the courts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The courts went on for about a good few hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then eventually, they found that everybody in court spoke French.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they won't need a Russian interpreter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody spoke French.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were told, you mustn't loot from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can requisition, but you mustn't loot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after that, I went to have a haircut.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
